token.name: Aave Token
token.description: Aave is a decentralized money market where users can lend and borrow more than 25 different crypto assets. Lenders can earn interest by providing liquidity to the market, while borrowers can borrow by collateralizing their cryptoassets to take out loans from the liquidity pools. AAVE tokens are used for protocol governance and can be staked for protocol fees in exchange for providing an insurance backstop.
